validationRules.instruction: [Cases treated] should be less than or equal to the number of [Suspected malaria cases]. Both numbers can be zeros.
validationRules.name: Cases treated <= Suspected malaria cases

validationRules.instruction: [Malaria deaths] should be less than or equal to the number of [Malaria inpatients]. Both numbers can be zeros.
validationRules.name: Malaria deaths <= Malaria inpatients

validationRules.instruction: [Malaria deaths] should be less than or equal to the number of [all-cause deaths]. Both numbers can be zeros.
validationRules.name: Malaria deaths <= all-cause deaths

validationRules.instruction: [Malaria inpatients] should be less than or equal to the number of [all-cause outpatient]. Both numbers can be zeros.
validationRules.name: Malaria inpatients <= all-cause outpatient

validationRules.instruction: [Number of ACT treatment courses receive] should be less than or equal to the number of [Number 1st-line treatment courses received (inlc. ACTs)]. Both numbers can be zeros.

leftSide.description: Number of ACT treatment courses receive

validationRules.name: Number of ACT treatment courses receive <= Number 1st-line treatment courses received (inlc. ACTs)

validationRules.instruction: [Number of ANC visits] should be greater than or equal to the number of [Number of SP course received for IPTp]. Both numbers can be zeros.
validationRules.name: Number of ANC visits >= Number of SP course received for IPTp

rightSide.description: Number of SP course received for IPTp

validationRules.instruction: [Outpatient malaria cases (confirmed + presumed)] should be less than or equal to the number of [Suspected malaria cases]. Both numbers can be zeros.
validationRules.name: Outpatient malaria cases (confirmed + presumed) <= Suspected malaria cases

validationRules.instruction: [Outpatient malaria cases (confirmed + presumed)] should be less than or equal to the number of [all-cause outpatient]. Both numbers can be zeros.
validationRules.name: Outpatient malaria cases (confirmed + presumed) <= all-cause outpatient

validationRules.instruction: [Outpatient malaria cases (confirmed + presumed)] should be greater than or equal to the number of [Positive (Micr)] + [Positive (RDT)]. Both numbers can be zeros.
validationRules.name: Outpatient malaria cases (confirmed + presumed) >= Positive (Micr)

validationRules.instruction: [Positive (Micr)] should be less than or equal to the number of [Tested (Micr)]. Both numbers can be zeros.
validationRules.name: Positive (Micr) <= Tested (Micr)

validationRules.instruction: [Positive (Micr)] should be equal the sum of [P. falciparum (Micr)] + [P. vivax (Micr)] + [Mixed (Micr)] +[Other (Micr)]
validationRules.name: Positive (Micr) = Sum of species (Pf, Pv, Mixed, Other species)

validationRules.instruction: [Positive (RDT)] should be less than or equal to the number of [Tested (RDT)]. Both numbers can be zeros.
validationRules.name: Positive (RDT) <= Tested (RDT)

validationRules.instruction: [Positive (RDT)] should be equal the number of [P. falciparum (RDT)]. Both numbers can be zeros.
validationRules.name: Positive (RDT) = Sum of species (RDT)

validationRules.instruction: [all-cause admission] should be less than or equal to the number of [all-cause outpatient]. Both numbers can be zeros.
validationRules.name: all-cause admission <= all-cause outpatient

validationRules.instruction: [all-cause deaths] should be less than or equal to the number of [all-cause admission]. Both numbers can be zeros.
validationRules.name: all-cause deaths <= all-cause admission
